author: COMSOL
description: This example studies adsorption of two proteins in an ion-exchange column. The adsorption is described by equilibrium reactions. First, the kinetics are studied in a 0D model with the Reaction Engineering interface. Second, a 3D model is used to examine the adsorption within the porous structure of the ion-exchange mass.
